{"description":"Al is my guy, 100%. There are some people in this space that stand out in your community, and Al is one of them.

I am beyond grateful to know Al and have him be a massive part of my community. 

We need more ALs!"}

{"description":"Papasmooth is one of a very few who has been here with us since day 1 when abstract is only the concept transitioning from testnet to mainnet

I could personally say that he truly deserves gigachad where he continues to spread positive and supportive energy 

I wish you the best brother"}

{"description":"Aliru is very present within the Abstract ecosystem, he is an active Gigachad, often there to help the community.

He brings his touch of freshness and originality.

I appreciate him for his authenticity."}

{"description":"I first met AL through Abstract, and we’ve talked a bunch on X since then always vibing, always supporting each other in the Abstract community. AL is honestly one of the most dedicated Giga Chads I’ve met. His love for Abstract and Penguins is on another level.

He’s always dropping quality, positive content about Abstract and Pudgy Penguins on X. If you’re new to either community, AL is 100% someone you should follow and learn from.

Keep being a legend and spreading that good energy, AL."}

{
  "description": "Ich kenne Mic von Final Bosu Community, er ist immer supportive und ist auch active in discord channels."
}

{
  "description": "Known AL a while through Pudgy Penguins and he supported me in my early days of streaming. He's honest, kind and a great person within the ecosystem and beyond. \n\nA genuine human being (and penguin)."
}

{
  "description": "did grab a 3 calls with guezito, cuteinvestment, and jampzey as I found human verification a good experiences to get to talk with people with same interest around the world\n\nwe might never get to hop into the same call and continue to text or supporting each other on CT (many won't be joining IRL event) so I kinda feel good this initiative lead us to connect and verify who is the real human",
  "source": "broker"
}

{
  "description": "Red is super well-known as core community member on Green chain. His Giga chad badge says it more then any of my words. Been like a balm for my ears to hear his thoughts about getting Giga Chad role, that never focus on it personally, he is using all advantages on portal, like streaming, trading, gaming, collecting"
}

{
  "description": "I met sillybilly through onchain heroes. 

sillybilly is an ideal example of what a great community member looks like. his content is great, he shows up and is always positive in the discord/timeline. 

we are very lucky to have him around as a friend"
}

{
  "description": "Cristian leads with love and positivity. His presence makes you feel warm and welcome in any community he is a part of. I had the great pleasure of meeting him in person at NFT NYC, and that only reinforced what I felt online. He is a gifted content creator who is able to pivot seamlessly from providing thoughtful analysis to contagious laughter. I know he's someone I'll vibe with for many years to come. I've recently learned more about his expertise beyond crypto, and it only deepened my respect for him. Bonus Fact: Cristian is a pro Twerker!"
}

{
  "description": "Genuine Giga Chad carries Abstract blood in his veins\nGiga Chad is a true Abstract bloodline. We have known each other for quite a long time at Abstract, honestly I always appreciate what he brings and spreads to the Abstract community."
}

{
  "description": "I first met Saucii at Abstract and was in awe of the energy and culture he brought to the Abstract community. Always supportive and creating a vibe for the community. Appreciate everything you do brother."
}

{"description":"AL is an incredible guy. He's always super supportive of others in the Igloo and the extended pudgy community, a well as Abstract.

I find joy watching his journey in Web3 and how he includes his family, his lifestyle creating content for his audience.

I wish there were more people like AL!"}

{
  "description": "MIC and I first crossed paths on Abstract through a handful of shared projects, but it wasn’t until we connected more deeply in Moonbirds that I realized just how much he elevates a community. He shows up with positivity, insight, and a genuine desire to help the people around him grow. His involvement in the Solana ecosystem even inspired me to revisit trading platforms. MIC has given me confidence that the right tools can truly elevate my trading approach, rather than relying solely on raw ability. I’m grateful our paths keep crossing, and I’m excited to continue building alongside him."
}
